ivardefs.name: etag
ivardefs.desc: The Etag for the resource, if the operation for the entry produced a versioned resource (see [Resource Metadata and Versioning](http.html#versioning) and [Managing Resource Contention](http.html#concurrency)).

ivardefs.name: lastModified
ivardefs.desc: The date/time that the resource was modified on the server.

ivardefs.name: location
ivardefs.desc: The location header created by processing this operation, populated if the operation returns a location.

ivardefs.name: outcome
ivardefs.desc: An OperationOutcome containing hints and warnings produced as part of processing this entry in a batch or transaction.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status code returned by processing this entry. The status SHALL start with a 3 digit HTTP code (e.g. 404) and may contain the standard HTTP description associated with the status code.

properties.desc: Indicates the results of processing the corresponding 'request' entry in the batch or transaction being responded to or what the results of an operation where when returning history.
